{"tid":753051,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"四川水災　港賑災基金速撥53.6萬元援助","createTime":"2018-07-23T09:53:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-23T15:22:03.000Z","uid":54517,"like":2,"dislike":128,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"97fa6b8029ab836a69440276555993ba93a4ed93","tid":753051,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T09:53:45.000Z","msg":"四川近日遭遇數十年來罕見暴雨，數十萬人受災，直接經濟損失數以億元人民幣計。香港特區政府宣布，從賑災基金撥出53.6萬元予愛德基金會（香港），賑濟內地四川省水災災民。<br />\n<br />\n該撥款是按賑災基金諮詢委員會設立的快速審批撥款申請機制批出，旨在加快處理撥款申請，讓救援機構在災禍發生後第一時間賑災。<br />\n<br />\n港府表示，撥款會用來為水災災民提供大米及食油，為確保撥款用於指定用途，委員會將要求愛德基金會（香港）完成賑災計劃後，呈交評估報告及經審核帳目。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180723/s00001/1532329747200\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180723%2Fs00001%2F1532329747200&d=ZxeHy217KvZL1YY2zO4x2f7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=e3a91aff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180723%2Fs00001%2F1532329747200&h=b83746be\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180723/s00001/1532329747200</a><br />\n<br />\n厲害了我的國<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50fe07f1ec762eb5cb0134321e3c91fa3833b08c","tid":753051,"uid":47083,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T09:54:17.000Z","msg":"仆街啦"},{"pid":"b5c14ba7031c7bc79219dd26c0ae3188aee515b2","tid":753051,"uid":54517,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"50fe07f1ec762eb5cb0134321e3c91fa3833b08c","tid":753051,"uid":47083,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T09:54:17.000Z","msg":"仆街啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T09:56:35.000Z","msg":"又射咗幾十萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f45e077619e733c3244509dff9ee37f7e78c1fd","tid":753051,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"r